---
import '../../styles/global.css';
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const title = 'Robert T. Hernandez | Personal Injury Attorney';
const description = 'Robert T. Hernandez is a Las Vegas native and personal injury attorney at Eric Blank Injury Attorneys, drawing on a decade of civil-defense experience to represent injured clients.';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={title} description={description} />
  </head>
  <body class="overflow-x-clip">
    <Header />
    <main>
      <section class="bg-brand-navy text-white">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:py-20 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-gold mb-3">Our Attorneys</p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Robert T. Hernandez</h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-200">Personal Injury Attorney</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
          <div class="space-y-10 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <img src="/Robert-Hernandez.png" alt="Robert T. Hernandez" width="537" height="427" loading="lazy" class="w-full max-w-xs h-auto rounded-lg" />

            <p>Robert is a Las Vegas native with deep ties to Nevada. A first-generation Mexican American born and raised in Las Vegas, he completed his undergraduate studies at the University of Nevada, Reno (cum laude). Thereafter, Robert returned to Las Vegas, where he earned his law degree at the William S. Boyd School of Law at UNLV. Since then, he has spent his entire legal career in Las Vegas and practiced in a variety of civil law fields, including personal injury, intentional torts, HOA disputes, and construction defect.</p>

            <p>During the first 10 years of Robert’s career, he worked for several civil defense firms where he honed his legal skills and gained insider knowledge about insurance company strategies and tactics. Robert now uses this knowledge to serve his clients and ensure excellent legal representation.</p>

            <p>Robert has represented thousands of clients with successful results in both small and large matters. He values his clients and believes that they all deserve respect and earnest representation regardless of the dollar value. Robert joined the personal injury team at Eric Blank Injury Attorneys because of their mutual dedication to the highest-quality legal representation.</p>

            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Education</h2>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li>J.D., William S. Boyd School of Law, University of Nevada, Las Vegas</li>
                <li>B.A., University of Nevada, Reno (cum laude)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Admission</h2>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li><a href="https://www.nvbar.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-navy underline">Nevada</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
